## Form Components

### Text Inputs
```tsx
<Input
  type="email"
  name="email"
  label="Email"
  registerProps={register("email", { required: true })}
  error={errors.email}
/>
```

### Text Area
```tsx
<Input
  type="text"
  autosizeTextarea
  rows={3}
  name="message"
  placeholder="Paste in email content"
  registerProps={register("message", { required: true })}
  error={errors.message}
/>
```

